titleInfo.title: SE Property Holdings, LLC v. Sandy Creek II, LLC et al
titleInfo.subTitle: Order granting in part denying in part 143 MOTION for Attorney Fees filed by SE Property Holdings, LLC. SEPHs Petition for Attorneys Fees and Costs is DENIED without prejudice as to Defendants Pidikiti and CIP and GRANTED in part and DENIED in part as to Defendants SC II and Skipper, such that SEPH is awarded $230,465.50 in attorneys fees and $4,954.18 in costs and expenses from these Defendants; and to assist the Court in preparing a final judgment against SC II and Skipper, SEPH shall file, on or before Tuesday, January 14, 2014, a document including the amount of principal and interest, as set out. Defendants shall file any objection to said document on or before Tuesday, January 21, 2014. If no such objection is filed, the Court will treat the amounts claimed by SEPH as unopposed and will enter final judgment accordingly. Signed by Judge Kristi K. DuBose on 1/7/2014. (cmj)
